MBOMBELA: A video is spreading on social media and WhatsApp of a young man falling off the back of what appears to be a game-viewer bakkie, at the traffic light next to Absa Square.The incident appears to have taken place on the corner of Samora Machel Drive and Paul Kruger StreetThe incident happened at night while two young men were sitting on the back as one was recording a video message from the vehicle as it drove through town.No further information about the event is available at present but residents are reminded to be cautious on the roads and familiarise themselves with the new legislation regarding transportation on the back of open vehicles on public roads.